Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Anniversaries to remember
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xkqj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Apr 1985
Uproar over president's anniversary plans to visit German war cemetery but not a concentration camp. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less